div.div: Commented on #1074 Polycentric comments aren't posted

@ericcox Keep in mind, polycentric comments have nothing to do with Youtube and Youtube has no control over them. They can only censor platform comments, which you can't post with GrayJay anyway. The timeout to the *.polycentric.io domain can only mean two things, either it's actually a network timeout (your device can't send the comment packet to the polycentric server in time for some reason) or the packet reaches the polycentric server but it takes too long to process it and gives up
